       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6CL02.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-INPUTS.
           05  WS-ELAPSED-DAYS       PIC 9(2) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-DAY-TABLE.
               10  WS-DAY-TYPE      PIC X OCCURS 31 TIMES.
       01  WS-COUNTERS.
           05  WS-DAY-INDEX          PIC 9(2) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-WORKING-DAYS       PIC 9(2) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-DELAY-DAYS         PIC S9(3) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-PENALTY-AMT        PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-ELAPSED-DAYS
           PERFORM 2100-COUNT-WORKING-DAYS
           DISPLAY WS-PENALTY-AMT
           STOP RUN.
       2100-COUNT-WORKING-DAYS.
           PERFORM VARYING WS-DAY-INDEX FROM 1 BY 1
              UNTIL WS-DAY-INDEX > WS-ELAPSED-DAYS
              IF WS-DAY-TYPE(WS-DAY-INDEX) = 'W'
                 ADD 1 TO WS-WORKING-DAYS
              END-IF
           END-PERFORM
           COMPUTE WS-DELAY-DAYS = WS-WORKING-DAYS - 7
           IF WS-DELAY-DAYS > ZERO
              COMPUTE WS-PENALTY-AMT = WS-DELAY-DAYS * 500
           END-IF.
